==English==

===Adjective===
{{en-adj-more}}

# Lacking in [[intelligence]]. Also, exhibiting the quality of having been done by someone lacking in intelligence.
#: ''Changing these sample sentences to those that do not make sense is a  '''stupid''' thing to do.''
# To the point of [[stupor]].
#: ''Neurobiology bores me '''stupid'''.''
# {{slang}} {{archaic}} Extremely.
#: ''My gear is '''stupid''' fly.''
# {{slang}} Amazing.
#: ''That [[dunk]] was '''stupid!''' His head was above the rim!''

